descriptions.direction: Located in Hulhumalé, Coral Grand Beach & Spa is near the beach. Banana Reef Dive Site and Victory Wreck Dive Site are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Hulhumalé Central Park and Hulhumale Beach.
descriptions.general: Ideally located in the Malé International Airport area, Coral Grand Beach & Spa promises a relaxing and wonderful visit. Whether traveling for business or leisure, guests can enjoy the hotel's excellent facilities and services, including free Wi-Fi in all rooms, 24-hour security, daily housekeeping, private check-in/check-out, and taxi service. Well-appointed guest rooms feature flat-screen televisions, complimentary instant coffee and tea, and a free welcome drink. Guests can enjoy various water sports activities such as boating, canoeing, and snorkeling, as well as the outdoor pool. Experience a welcoming atmosphere and excellent service at Coral Grand Beach & Spa.
